criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  1.born at study hospital;

          -  2. singleton birth;

          -  3. less than 28 weeks GA

          -  4.Signed informed consent obtained;

          -  5. Umbilical cord blood collection and testing qualified; 6.Diagnosed with BPD

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  1. with severe congenital abnormalities;

          -  2.with maternal clinical chorioamnionitis

          -  3. the mother was positive for hepatitis B (HBsAg and/or HBeAg) or C virus (anti-HCV),
             syphilis, HIV (anti-HIV-1 and -2) or IgM against cytomegalovirus, rubella, toxoplasma
             and herpes simplex virus.
